@Comment:	Chi and Mot don't really play together at all; Chi plays while Mot looks on. Still , there is a pleasant atmosphere and Mot seems to be proud of Chi. The only mention of the properties of magnets is when Mot says <remember the different sides of a magnet , Chi>. Chi experiments a little with the magnets on her own , noticing when certain pieces don't stick. EXP's participation , through comments and laughter during particular situations , isn't extensive but it is almost as much as Mot's. Video does not start until later; transcription until then is solely from audio
*INV:	www .
